</li><li>Ega theatres <a href="http://www.egacinemas.com/New/Default.aspx" class="external autonumber" rel="nofollow">[42]</a>, p.h road, Kilpauk (Features Hindi movies).
</li><li>Sangam cine complex in kilpauk. For tickets check www.ticketnew.com.
