<ul><li><span class='vcard' id = 'Stores_on_Doors'><span class="fn org">Stores on Doors</span> (<span class="nickname">Best Online Shop in Chennai for Grocery, Vegetables and Fruits</span>), <span class="adr"><span class="street-address">171/4, Pallavan Street, Alwarthirunagar, Chennai</span></span> (<span class="note directions">www.storesondoors.com</span>), <span class="tel"><abbr class="type" title="voice">☎</abbr> <span class="phone value">044 65158534</span></span>, <a class="url external autonumber" href="http://www.storesondoors.com" rel="nofollow">[49]</a>. &#160;<a class="listing-edit" href="#Stores_on_Doors" onclick="editListing('Stores_on_Doors', 'buy', 'Chennai');return false;" title="click to edit Stores on Doors" rel="nofollow">edit</a></span>
