<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/wiki/en/index.php?title=Chennai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=40" title="Edit section: Art galleries">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Art_galleries">Art galleries</span></h3>
