<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/wiki/en/index.php?title=Chennai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=66" title="Edit section: Money changers">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Money_changers">Money changers</span></h3>
<p>Many hotels will change money for you at the front desk.  However, they may not have the best rates.
</p><p>It is best to change money at the city based money changers than the ones located at the airports. The ones at the airport offer much less for exchanging forex into Indian Rupees and sell forex for a much higher rate than the market rate.
</p>
<ul><li><b>American Express</b>, Spencers Plaza, Anna salai
</li><li><b>Thomas Cook</b>, Spencers Plaza, Anna salai
</li></ul>
